id: pm-umhv
title: Add scoped audit override mode for pm update metadata mutations
description: Implement a non-owner metadata-only override path for pm update that avoids broad force semantics while preserving lifecycle safety.
type: Task
status: in_progress
priority: 1
tags[4]: governance,ownership,pm-cli,update
created_at: "2026-04-06T16:46:58.842Z"
updated_at: "2026-04-07T18:24:05.498Z"
author: codex-agent
acceptance_criteria: pm update supports a scoped --allow-audit-update mode for approved metadata fields on cross-owner items; lifecycle fields remain protected; output and history label audit override usage deterministically.
parent: pm-lwps
comments[6]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-04-06T16:46:58.842Z",codex-agent,Duplicate-check evidence used pm context pm search and open or in-progress lists. Net-new scope under pm-lwps for scoped metadata ownership override without duplicate tracking item.
  "2026-04-06T17:08:51.634Z",codex-agent,"Progress: implemented scoped --allow-audit-update path for pm update with metadata-only guardrails and explicit update_audit history labeling. Ownership bypass now routes through mutateItem only when allow-audit-update is set; lifecycle and linkage flags are rejected in audit mode to preserve status and close semantics."
  "2026-04-06T17:08:55.120Z",codex-agent,"Verification evidence: node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/update-command.spec.ts tests/unit/update-many-command.spec.ts tests/unit/completion-command.spec.ts tests/unit/pi-agent-extension.spec.ts tests/integration/release-readiness-runtime.spec.ts passed (140 tests)."
  "2026-04-06T18:46:39.466Z",codex-agent,"Delivered ownership-safe audit update mode: wired --allow-audit-update across CLI normalization/contracts/Pi mapping, enforced metadata-only scope guardrails for lifecycle/linkage fields, and validated deterministic audit_update result tagging/history labeling. Verification: pnpm build; node scripts/run-tests.mjs test; node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage."
  "2026-04-07T18:14:16.161Z",codex-agent,"2026-04-07 scope extension: introduce explicit dependency-audit override path (--allow-audit-dep-update) for cross-owner append-only dependency mutations; retain strict protection against unrelated lifecycle mutations without force. Planned files: src/cli/main.ts, src/cli/commands/update.ts, tests/unit/update-command.spec.ts, docs/AGENTS+README+PRD."
  "2026-04-07T18:24:05.498Z",codex-agent,"Implementation progress: added explicit --allow-audit-dep-update mode for cross-owner append-only dependency additions. Scope enforcement now allows only --dep and rejects lifecycle/metadata/clear/replace/remove flags; audit runs continue to use update_audit op labeling with assignee-conflict bypass for ownership-safe attribution. Added regression tests in tests/unit/update-command.spec.ts for success and guardrail failures."
